data.description: This charming ranch home is very comfortable and inviting, with hardwood floors throughout, tons of natural light, built-in shelving, and updated kitchen and bathrooms. The large front porch, complete with a swing, is perfect for relaxing and taking in the fresh air. There is a long driveway and a detached garage for private parking and storage. The fully fenced yard offers privacy and space for outdoor activities. Many features were updated in 2016 including the HVAC, hot water heater, roof, windows, kitchen and bathrooms. Centrally located nears restaurants, shops, bases and entertainment, this home is sure to please!
